00:39:48.510 --> 00:39:53.510
Kili Ad will continue to fulfill its mandate to train new missionaries.

00:39:53.510 --> 00:39:55.510
South Africa area.

00:39:55.510 --> 00:39:58.510
All dedicated Christians will continue to work

00:39:58.510 --> 00:40:00.510
with the missionary spirit.

