To seek out the meek hearted until Jehovah says,

00:40:03.510 --> 00:40:05.510
the work is done.

00:40:05.510 --> 00:40:08.510
For more than 50 years,

00:40:08.510 --> 00:40:13.510
Kili Ad has had an impact on the worldwide preaching work.

00:40:13.510 --> 00:40:17.510
It continues to prepare young men and women for missionary service,

00:40:17.510 --> 00:40:21.510
and it's wonderful to reflect on what they accomplish.

00:40:21.510 --> 00:40:25.510
Thanks to their efforts and with Jehovah's blessing,

00:40:25.510 --> 00:40:29.510
great numbers in many lands continue to be helped

00:40:29.510 --> 00:40:32.510
to gain the knowledge of the truth.

00:40:32.510 --> 00:40:36.510
This is the legacy that Kili Ad is leaving behind.

00:40:36.510 --> 00:40:40.510
It is something that will never be forgotten.
